ht charisma field.  Just finished grandmaster jewlers eyeglass and now have int and cha to 285.  some nice quests for a young enchanter are the incandescent mask and the 12 cha rod quest of which i cant rememberthe name of &lt;sigh&gt;.  before the eyeglass i would have to switch out an item or 2 to get cha up to my limit but would always do this for charming.<br>
