Max possible CHA at level 65 w. NO Planar Power = 280<br>
Max possible CHA at level 65 w. MAX Planar Power = 305<br>
<br>
... and for arguments sake;<br>
<br>
Max possible INT / WIS at level 60 = 255<br>
Max possible INT / WIS at level 65 w. NO Planar Power = 280<br>
Max possible INT / WIS at level 65 w. MAX Planar Power = 305<br>
Max possible INT / WIS at level 65 w. MAX  Innate Enlightment= 355<br>
<br>
Its no big secret, can all be read inside the game =)<br>
